  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Vine</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Vines</b> are a resource in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC. They are dropped from chopping a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Viney_Bush\" title=\"Viney Bush\">Viney Bush</a> with a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Machete\" title=\"Machete\">Machete</a> or by digging one up with a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shovel\" title=\"Shovel\">Shovel</a>. Vines are used in several crafting recipes.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hamlet\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet_icon\" title=\"Hamlet icon\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Hamlet</span></h2>\n<p>Vines are also included in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC, it can  be obtained by killing <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Snaptooth_Seedling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Snaptooth Seedling\">Snaptooth Seedlings</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Snaptooth_Flytrap\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Snaptooth Flytrap\">Snaptooth Flytraps</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bramble_Bloom\" title=\"Bramble Bloom\">Bramble Blooms</a>. Using a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shears\" title=\"Shears\">Shears</a> on a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Viney_Bush\" title=\"Viney Bush\">Viney Bush</a> will result in 2 <b>Vines</b> instead of the usual one.\n</p>\n",
