  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Dây leo là một tài nguyên trong Shipwrecked DLC. Chúng rơi ra khi chặt Bụi Nho bằng Dao Rựa hoặc đào lên bằng Xẻng. Cây nho được sử dụng trong một số công thức chế tạo.</p>",
  "title": "Vine",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{Item Infobox\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 45 sec\n|stack = 40\n|droppedBy = {{pic|28|Viney Bush}} ({{pic|24|Machete}}{{pic|24|Shears}})<br>{{Pic32|Blue Whale Carcass}} {{Pic32|White Whale Carcass}}<br>{{Pic|32|Snaptooth Seedling}} {{Pic|32|Snaptooth Flytrap}} {{Pic|24|Bramble Bloom}} ({{Pic|24|Hamlet icon|Hamlet}})\n|spawnCode = \"vine\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wilson = Maybe I can tie stuff up with this.\n|willow = I could use this for something. Or I could just burn it.\n|wolfgang = For string enemies together.\n|wendy = Unruly life.\n|wx78 = UNRULY NATURE\n|wickerbottom = A common jungle vine.\n|woodie = Sigh. Not a tree.\n|maxwell = It's twisted and gnarled.\n|wagstaff = A ropey branch. I can think of nine good uses for it already.\n|wigfrid = What can yöu dö för me?\n|webber = This stuff is wild.\n|walani = Good for lashing stuff down.\n|warly = Not a single grape on it...\n|woodlegs = Them's be th'stranglin' kind.\n|wilba = FAST BIND, FAST FIND\n|wormwood = String branches\n|wheeler = The kind of thing that would be more useful if I had a bunch of them.\n|choose = warly}}\n'''Vines''' are a resource in the ''[[Shipwrecked]]'' DLC. They are dropped from chopping a [[Viney Bush]] with a [[Machete]] or by digging one up with a [[Shovel]]. Vines are used in several crafting recipes.\n\n=={{Pic|32|Hamlet icon}} Hamlet==\nVines are also included in the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC, it can  be obtained by killing [[Snaptooth Seedling]]s, [[Snaptooth Flytrap]]s and [[Bramble Bloom]]s. Using a [[Shears]] on a [[Viney Bush]] will result in 2 '''Vines''' instead of the usual one.\n\n=={{Pic32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Bamboo\n|count2 = 4\n|result = Raft}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Boards\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Row Boat}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Bamboo\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Palm Leaf\n|count3 = 4\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Thatch Sail}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Cloth\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Empty Bottle\n|count3 = 3\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Life Jacket}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|item2 = Bamboo\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Seaweed\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Mussel Stick}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Snakeskin\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Bone Shards\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Snakeskin Jacket}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Shark Fin\n|item3 = Coconut\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Sleek Hat}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Seaweed\n|count2 = 5\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 2\n|item3 = Shark Gills\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Sea Sack}}\n{{Recipe\n|item2 = Cloth\n|item1 = Vine\n|count1 = 3\n|item3 = Cork\n|count3 = 6\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Pith Hat\n|dlc = Hamlet}}\n{{Resources}}\n\n[[pl:Winorośl (DSS)]]\n[[vi:Cành Leo]]\n[[Category:Items]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Resources]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Mob Dropped Items]]"
